                                                                                    <div data-comida="a-calda" class="accordeon">
                            <h2>Como preparar a Calda</h2>
                            <p>Modo de Preparo em 4 passos.</p>
                            <button aria-label="Abrir/Esconder preparo"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div data-comida="a-calda" class="accordeon-text">
                            <ol>
                                                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-1-passo-1">Passo 1 </h3>
                                            <p>Vamos começar com a calda: em uma panela coloque o açúcar e leve em fogo médio mexendo até derreter por completo;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-1.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-1.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 1" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-1.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-1.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 1" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-1-passo-2">Passo 2 </h3>
                                            <p>Em seguida adicione a água e continue mexendo até derreter todas as pelotas de açúcar;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-2.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-2.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 2" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-2.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-2.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 2" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-1-passo-3">Passo 3 </h3>
                                            <p>Transfira essa calda para uma forma untada com manteiga ou margarina e espalhe o coco em flocos por cima;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-3.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-3.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 3" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-3.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-3.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 3" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-1-passo-4">Passo 4 </h3>
                                            <p>Reserve a forma com a calda.</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-12.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-12.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 4" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-12.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-12.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 4" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                </ol>
                        </div>
                                                                    <div data-comida="o-bolo" class="accordeon">
                            <h2>Como preparar o Bolo</h2>
                            <p>Modo de Preparo em 8 passos.</p>
                            <button aria-label="Abrir/Esconder preparo"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div data-comida="o-bolo" class="accordeon-text">
                            <ol>
                                                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-1">Passo 1 </h3>
                                            <p>Para a massa do bolo pegue um liquidificador e coloque os ovos, o leite de coco, o óleo, o açúcar e bata por 2 minutos;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-4.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-4.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 1" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-4.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-4.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 1" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-2">Passo 2 </h3>
                                            <p>Transfira para uma tigela e vá adicionando a farinha de trigo aos poucos;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-5.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-5.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 2" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-5.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-5.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 2" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-3">Passo 3 </h3>
                                            <p>Mexa bem até ficar bem homogêneo;</p>
                                                                                            <div class="only-desktop" style="margin-top: 20px">
                                                    <div class="textwidget custom-html-widget"></div>                                                                                                    </div>
                                                <div class="only-mobile" style="margin-top: 20px">
                                                    <div class="textwidget custom-html-widget"></div>                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-11.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-11.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 3" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-11.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-11.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 3" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-4">Passo 4 </h3>
                                            <p>Acrescente o coco ralado e misture bem;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-6.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-6.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 4" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-6.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-6.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 4" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-5">Passo 5 </h3>
                                            <p>Por último coloque o fermento em pó e mexa;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-7.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-7.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 5" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-7.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-7.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 5" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-6">Passo 6 </h3>
                                            <p>Despeje essa mistura na forma com calda que foi reservada;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-8.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-8.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 6" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-8.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-8.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 6" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-7">Passo 7 </h3>
                                            <p>Leve para assar em forno pré aquecido a 180ºC por cerca de 40-50 minutos ou até dourar;</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-9.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-9.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 7" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-9.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-9.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 7" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                                    <li>
                                            <h3 id="etapa-2-passo-8">Passo 8 </h3>
                                            <p>Retire do forno, espere amornar para desenformar e servir.</p>
                                                                                                                                        <a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-10.jpg">
                                                    <picture><source srcset="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/doc-root/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-10.jpg.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="699px" height="699px" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20699%20699'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 8" class="webpexpress-processed" data-lazy-src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-10.jpg"><noscript><img width="699px" height="699px" loading="lazy" src="https://comidinhasdochef.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Bolo-Cocada-Invertido-10.jpg" alt="Bolo Cocada Invertido - Passo 8" class="webpexpress-processed"></noscript></picture>
                                                </a>
                                                                                    </li>
                                                                                                </ol>
                        </div>
                                                    <div class="resume">
                    <p><b>Tags:</b> Bolo Cocada Invertido </p>
                                    </div>
