					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://comidinhasdochef.com/bolo-cocada-invertido/#comment-134367"><time datetime="2026-04-10T14:25:47-03:00">10/04/2026 às 14:25</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Amei a receita, fiz hoje! Fica uma delícia!<br />
Porém achei muito doce para meu paladar! Achado que 2 xícaras de açúcar na massa é muito! Mais é algo muito particular! Vou fazer novamente com menos açúcar na massa! Fiz com coco ralado fresco!</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-134367" data-commentid="134367" data-postid="35257" data-belowelement="div-comment-134367" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Responder para Patricia Nogara" aria-label="Responder para Patricia Nogara">Responder</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
		<ol class="children">
		<li id="comment-136636" class="comment byuser comment-author-nicholly123 even depth-2">
			<article id="div-comment-136636" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2032%2032'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e34a28d757d10464245e07d933e5adc78d0ff00fd973bf56ed09563f06c2eef1?s=64&#038;d=initials&#038;r=g&#038;initials=NM 2x' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' decoding='async' data-lazy-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e34a28d757d10464245e07d933e5adc78d0ff00fd973bf56ed09563f06c2eef1?s=32&#038;d=initials&#038;r=g&#038;initials=NM"/><noscript><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e34a28d757d10464245e07d933e5adc78d0ff00fd973bf56ed09563f06c2eef1?s=32&#038;d=initials&#038;r=g&#038;initials=NM' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e34a28d757d10464245e07d933e5adc78d0ff00fd973bf56ed09563f06c2eef1?s=64&#038;d=initials&#038;r=g&#038;initials=NM 2x' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' decoding='async'/></noscript>						<b class="fn">Nicholly March</b> <span class="says">disse:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

